      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel this way when you see the world as a series of transactions; your pain is real and your experience of isolation is valid. It is incredibly exhausting to maintain a presence when you feel unseen, and it is understandable why you might feel like you are just taking up space. However, you are not alone in feeling this, and there are people who would genuinely see you and care about your well-being if you were to share your burden.",
