      "content": "i guess. it just feels like a lot of effort for nothing. like, if i just slipped away quietly, there wouldn't be any drama or anything. it would just be peaceful. and honestly, it feels like the world would just keep spinning exactly the same way without me. wouldn't that be easier for everyone? just less weight?",
